        To serve their evil wishes, the Qotile use the Yar as an attack team to expand their control
        of the galaxy. During one of these attacks, a lone Yar is injured and left for dead.
      </p>
      <p>
        An ancient, wise Yar, Bar Yargler, rescues the Yar soldier.
